name: C. P. S. TRUST
briefDescription: C.P.S. TRUST is a Non-Government Voluntary Social organization working in Child Education, Child & women development programme, rural development, educational programme, environmental and women & girls welfare activities, S.H.G., Vocational Training Programme, Social Welfare Programme, Health Awareness Camp since last Two years and it is registered under the Indian Trust Act, 1882 in the year of 11/02/2016.Done NIESBUD program for 120 sc student, running project on ESDM and NDLM without any fees taken by the student
